    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/092b428e2281cd61e9c58f964189ec65.avif?t=1771509984\" width=1560 height=403 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/d98d62fe6de3de7d217a644ac47f4813.poster.avif?t=1771509984\" width=1170 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/d98d62fe6de3de7d217a644ac47f4813.webm?t=1771509984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/d98d62fe6de3de7d217a644ac47f4813.mp4?t=1771509984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位被委以重任在伦敦开设新餐厅的主厨需要做什么？没错，准备菜单并为餐厅取名。只是你几乎错过了截止日期。毫无头绪之际，你觉得自己超级幸运地看到了一封能解决你燃眉之急的邮件。你点击了附件中的链接，然后...欢迎来到仙境唯一的移动咖啡馆。你将与傲慢的猫咪展开一段漫长的旅程。祝你好运，希望你能找到回家的路。但首先，你得喂饱当地的居民。只是他们性格古怪，口味挑剔，还总爱干扰你烹饪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/2165bb187d4ee4ba92abca1b6c2a8bd0.poster.avif?t=1771509984\" width=1170 height=780 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/2165bb187d4ee4ba92abca1b6c2a8bd0.webm?t=1771509984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/2165bb187d4ee4ba92abca1b6c2a8bd0.mp4?t=1771509984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021530/extras/157d27b0cd259